    <tr>
     <td align="center" width="120" bgcolor="#dddddd"><font class="GraphicCaption">"Ordinarily I'd be upset that AAXP got nerfed, but I've gotten so many points off those LoS and Triton people that my skills are maxed anyway."</font></td>
     <td bgcolor="#ffffff"><img src="images/spacer.gif"></td>
